Prerequisite
---

The following packages should be installed in R: Rcpp RInside truncnorm stringr

Build and install in R
---

From the commande line:
  go to RMixtComp
  execute make

From Rstudio:
  open the project file RMixtComp/RMixtComp.Rproj
  press control + shift + b
  
Debug
---

When using the command-line make, a test program is created in RMixtComp/src/test . Executing it through gdb (via Eclipse for example) allows for easy debugging of RMixtComp.
